      "source": "; Generated by Web64 IDE. Edit the graphics asset, not this file.\ncharset_chars_size = $0800\n; Editor color references\ncharset_color_0 = 0\ncharset_background_color = 0\ncharset_color_1 = 5\ncharset_multicolor_1 = 5\ncharset_color_2 = 2\ncharset_multicolor_2 = 2\ncharset_color_3 = 1\ncharset_foreground_color = 1\ncharset_char_count = $0100\ncharset_chars_end = charset_chars + charset_chars_size\ncharset_char_0 = 0\ncharset_char_1 = 1\ncharset_char_2 = 2\ncharset_char_3 = 3\ncharset_char_4 = 4\ncharset_char_5 = 5\ncharset_char_6 = 6\ncharset_char_7 = 7\ncharset_char_8 = 8\ncharset_char_9 = 9\ncharset_char_10 = $0a\ncharset_char_11 = $0b\ncharset_char_12 = $0c\ncharset_char_13 = $0d\ncharset_char_14 = $0e\ncharset_char_15 = $0f\n"
